@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "Sassi di Matera & Calanchi | LIA NCC Tours";
}

<!-- Hero Section -->
<section class="relative h-screen w-full overflow-hidden flex items-center justify-center text-center">
    <div class="absolute inset-0 z-0">
        <img alt="Cinematic wide shot of Matera Sassi ancient city at dusk" class="w-full h-full object-cover cinematic-img" src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/aida-public/AB6AXuBd7q3AhslgLcmfBMcEsnhDx8T-fIMJhvHZpPxYi3N5LyVkBP8Iadn1M6EfhokdVbe4nqFQxy2utt2TjN0Uh0MaHokUAUkuXsEaLZ1bfCRlepuswN7CzmdHFCQMyegn-eV5sec4hBzxhYJREvucZ_hqQjwUW-a0yAyMaYS1s-WKCOd0GRrkYyQBp6EonPAJZ3f9jMKhtQNBJ1cL1JR-BvN1-xvR23yf-GAxc5g0D0tiOflbxH3zqHysrpSHD8DJf9tS2zY7rawlzoDx" />
        <div class="absolute inset-0 hero-mask"></div>
    </div>
    <div class="relative z-10 max-w-5xl px-6">
        <span class="font-bold text-primary tracking-[0.4em] uppercase text-xs mb-6 block">Esclusività Mediterranea</span>
        <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-6xl font-medium text-white mb-8 tracking-tight uppercase" style="letter-spacing: 4px;">Sassi di Matera <br /> &amp; Calanchi</h1>
        <div class="w-24 h-1 bg-[#D4AF37] mx-auto"></div>
    </div>
</section>
<main class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 md:px-16">
    <!-- L'Esperienza -->
    <section class="py-32 grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-center">
        <div class="space-y-10">
            <div class="text-left">
                <h2 class="text-4xl font-semibold text-white mb-4 section-title text-[24px]">L'Esperienza</h2>
                <div class="w-16 h-1 bg-[#D4AF37]"></div>
            </div>
            <div class="space-y-6 text-gray-400 font-light text-[15px] leading-relaxed">
                <p>Un viaggio nel tempo attraverso i Sassi di Matera, Patrimonio Mondiale dell'Umanità, dove la pietra racconta millenni di storia scolpita nel cuore della terra. Un'immersione totale nel silenzio mistico della Basilicata.</p>
                <p>Attraverseremo i Calanchi, cattedrali di argilla modellate dal vento, in un paesaggio lunare che ha ispirato registi e poeti. Con LIA NCC, ogni curva svela un segreto, ogni sosta è un momento di puro privilegio estetico.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="charcoal-border p-1 hover:border-[#D4AF37] transition-all duration-700 bg-black">
            <img alt="Detailed architectural view of stone dwellings in Matera" class="w-full h-[500px] object-cover" src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/aida-public/AB6AXuCm_E3LuAzl3c5We8jK6Ngff7L1F3WAGtES-C0Mc-KqE3ZqKjh5dsgw0Ij0N6QilEcv67q8CWzRng7dS9BfV-_MS4mvQlqh00I212n8f1foUrnib7D9V7Lx4gWaBtFh9CLJgVPIF_kCQMJGLWnbHSdXzyoH-A9CItC-LYrRStqYf6oEGGrXgWhNKViOD0ivjqsHPc5zFLk2v_j7t9mvT6PZE2v4WHmzAEtwgjDuKxzgCpwrYbRD8lUllVwfp2n3DMzzr0hmO-sX8C0C" />
        </div>
    </section>
